channel.title: What will happen at EOL
channel.description:
We are a current user of the Hosted Version of ReDash. We've successfully managed to now host this ourselves and will wait for EOL.
Do we need to do anything further for EOL? Can we actually suspend our Hosted Version earlier so we can confirm there are no hidden/unknown dependancies between ReDash Hosted and our own Hosted Versions?
Also at EOL, will billing just automatically stop?

item.title: What will happen at EOL
item.dc:creator: jesse
item.description:
VishVarsani:

Do we need to do anything further for EOL?

We can disable your account if you’d like to test this. Just reach out to us through the in-app support.

VishVarsani:

Also at EOL, will billing just automatically stop?

No one has been billed for hosted Redash since April. You will not be billed again.

Read full topic
